      "value": "<p>When working with textures inside of the Solaris context, you will need to manually convert your textures into the desired .tex file format for use with RenderMan.<br/><br/>This can easily be done by using the Texture Manager found by creating a new Solaris pane under RenderMan → Texture Manager </p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640896/RenderMan_TextureManager.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=535\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640896/RenderMan_TextureManager.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"733\" data-width=\"1231\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640910\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_TextureManager.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640896\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"35ee0101-e658-4109-85bc-a16402a3ee74\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640896/RenderMan_TextureManager.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1231&amp;height=733 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640896/RenderMan_TextureManager.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=535 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640896/RenderMan_Solaris_TextureManager.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082303&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=556\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640896/RenderMan_Solaris_TextureManager.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082303&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"668\" data-width=\"1081\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640913\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_TextureManager.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640896\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d1a92780-c50b-4a0e-8598-0a5a995e40c4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640896/RenderMan_Solaris_TextureManager.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082303&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1081&amp;height=668 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640896/RenderMan_Solaris_TextureManager.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433082303&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=556 1x\"></span><p /><p>More information about using the Texture Manager can be found <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-26.pixar.com/space/REN26/19661963/txmake\" rel=\"nofollow\">here </a></p>"
